# Branch discipline

Check `git branch --show-current` before editing. Keep unrelated work on separate branches.

## Active integration branches

| Branch | Purpose |
| --- | --- |
| `feature/offline-tenure` | Offline field app, tenure/evidence sync, Metro, SQLite persistence, related backend tenure parse |
| `chore/npm-workspaces` | npm workspaces monorepo (root install, unified lockfile, CI `-w` scripts) |
| `main` | Merged, deployable baseline |

## Rules

1. **Do not mix scopes** — tenure/evidence/offline changes belong on `feature/offline-tenure`; workspace/CI/root `package.json` changes belong on `chore/npm-workspaces`.
2. **Install location** — On `main` and `feature/offline-tenure` (pre-workspaces merge): `npm install` inside each app directory. On `chore/npm-workspaces` (and `main` after merge): `npm install` at repo root once.
3. **Before switching branches** — stash or commit WIP; resolve lockfile conflicts carefully (one root lockfile after workspaces merge).
4. **Rollback** — tag `pre-workspaces-2026-06-20` marks the last commit before workspaces adoption.

## Merge order (when ready)

1. Merge offline feature branch OR workspaces branch first (expect one lockfile conflict if both touched deps).
2. After workspaces lands on `main`, update Vercel install command to root `npm ci` for dashboard and marketing projects.
